	<span class="span-666 font16 bold_font margin-left-2" style="color:#BFB8E5;line-height:35px;">
		What is Dynonamics?
	</span>
	<span class="span-64 margin-left-3 margin-top-1" style="color:#BFB8E5;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;">
		<p>
			Dynonamics is a Heroku plugin, which scales your Dynos automatically according to your application's traffic.
			It helps reduce the unnecessary cost of Dynos and also prevents your application from request overloads.<br/><br/>
			Dynonamics is in the alpha testing phase right now. We offer the service for free during the alpha testing phrase. Therefore, please enjoy our service!
		</p>
	</span>
	<span class="span-666 hr margin-top-1">
	</span>
</span>
